XGenTask
public class VETexenTask
extends org.apache.velocity.texen.ant.TexenTask

An ant task for generating output by using VelocityEngine instead of the Velocity helper class. This task defines the default resourse loader to be "classpath". If a templatePath is defined, then the resourceLoader = "file, classloader".
